+#### Support Flow's 'implies' type guard variant (#16272 by @gkz)
+
+Adds support for Flow's `implies` type guard variant. Also updates the `flow-parser` dependency.
+
+<!-- prettier-ignore -->
+```jsx
+// Input
+declare function f(x: mixed): implies x is T;
+
+// Prettier stable
+// error
+
+// Prettier main
+declare function f(x: mixed): implies x is T;
+```
